text: Kaznakovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Tatar-Ulkanovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 77 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Tuymazy, 18 km from Tatar-Ulkanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kaznakovka
